          Heading link



 
Copy link



*Disclaimer: These facilities reserve the right to employ independent contractors in the Emergency Departments, which would be excluded from the network benefits described in the CampusCare Certificate of Coverage. All services received from independent contractors, at these facilities, will be processed as Out of Network at 100% of Usual & Customary plus applicable co-payments.








